    <Content contentid="3464" contenttypeid="STAFF" desc="Staff">
      <Description><![CDATA[One of the greatest advantages of staying in a villa is the personalised service provided by dedicated staff.&nbsp; The professionally trained staff at both Shinta Dewi villas take delight in offering warm and friendly Balinese hospitality, and know when to be on hand to help, or invisible when not required.]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Villa manager]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p>Shinta Dewi’s highly competent and friendly manager is responsible for the overall operation of both villas, and oversees and coordinates the staff in Seminyak and Ubud. </p>]]></Description>
