    <Content contentid="3476" contenttypeid="EHBD" desc="EH Bedroom Description">
      <Description><![CDATA[]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Guestrooms]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Large master suite with king-size bed (with trundle), dressing room and bathroom with twin basins, shower enclosure and bathtub</li><li>Two guest bedrooms opening onto second level veranda, each with beds that can be configured as a king or twins, and with a trundle for extra guests.</li><li> Garden level guest suite (with king or twin beds) can also be set up as a media room/study</li><li>The three ensuite guest bathrooms have twin basins and a large shower enclosure</li><li>All four bedrooms have both air-conditioning and ceiling fans, and are equipped with 32-inch TV, DVD player and a bar fridge</li></ul>]]></Description>
